Exclusively designed, private branded clothing for women
The Chico’s brand was founded in 1983 as a boutique selling Mexican folk art and cotton sweaters from a store on Florida’s Sanibel Island.


Home>Our Brands>Chico's









Chico's


Today, Chico’s primarily sells exclusively designed, private branded clothing for women featuring a combination of great style with on-trend, expressive and one-of-a-kind designs to yield a wardrobe that is fashionable, unique, relaxed, figure-flattering, and comfortable.
Chico’s currently operates more than 600 boutiques and over 100 outlets across the U.S., Canada, and Puerto Rico. Chico’s also publishes a monthly catalog and offers round-the-clock shopping at www.chicos.com.

















