Soma is So Much More than Sexy.
In 2004, a design team of women set out to create something they saw missing from the marketplace: a line that gives women what they really want. Bras as comfortable as they are beautiful. Panties that stay where they should. Pajamas that bring the softest sleep. The team began innovating, and they started Soma. Nearly 300 boutiques and millions of loyal customers later, Soma continues to improve women's lives every day through exceptional service and exclusive products. Because confidence is the sexiest thing a woman can wear. 


Home>Our Brands>Soma









Soma


The Soma brand, which began operations in 2004, sells on-trend lingerie, innovative and expertly fitted bras and panties, soft loungewear apparel, and exclusive beauty products. 
Soma currently operates over 270 boutiques and 19 outlets. Soma publishes its own catalog coinciding with key shopping periods and sells direct-to-consumer at www.soma.com.















