About Our Partnership
Chico’s FAS, Inc. is proud to support CMN Hospitals, a nonprofit organization that raises funds and awareness for 170 children’s hospitals throughout the United States and Canada. Since 2011, with the help of our caring customers and Associates, our Chico's FAS, Inc. family of brands has raised more than $8 million dollars for Children’s Miracle Network Hospitals®.
LEARN MORE










For more information, visit cmnhospitals.org

















For more information, visit cmnhospitals.org















