Chico's FAS, Inc., through its brands – Chico's, White House Black Market, and Soma Intimates, is a leading women's omni-channel specialty retailer of private branded, sophisticated, casual-to-dressy clothing, intimates, complementary accessories, and other non-clothing items. Under the Chico’s, White House Black Market, and Soma Intimates names, the company operates over 1,550 boutiques and outlets throughout the U.S. and Canada, as well as an online presence for each of our brands.
 



