Passport Program    Join the Family The Passport Program is Chico’s customer loyalty program. There is no fee to join or maintain membership in the Passport program. You may sign up for Passport online, at any U.S. Chico's boutique, or by phone at 888.855.4986 (TTY: 888.550.5559) by providing your first and last name, valid mailing address, phone number, email address and birth month. To receive your full benefits please provide your qualifying membership number every time you shop at Chico's. When your qualifying merchandise purchases reach $500 USD (whether it takes one day or three years) you will receive the full benefits of the Passport Program. Introductory Passport benefits include:  Be the first to know about newest collections, sales, and offers Preview new collections via email  Passport (once your merchandise purchases reach $500) benefits may include:  5% off every merchandise purchase (certain exclusions apply) Birthday bonuses Double discount days Invitations to special parties and events Private salesFree standard shipping within the continental U.S.  The Chico’s Passport Program is open to U.S. and International residents, excluding Canadian residents. Unfortunately, Canadian residents are not eligible for the Passport Program. If you are a Canadian resident, you may create an online account, but you will not be enrolled in our loyalty program. To be eligible for birthday bonus benefits, Passport members must have shopped with us during the past 12 months. No discount on purchases of gift cards, previously purchased merchandise, taxes, shipping and certain excluded merchandise. Participation in the program constitutes acceptance of current published terms and conditions. Each member is permitted one Passport membership only. Membership number is not transferable. Chico's reserves the right to modify or eliminate benefits without prior notice. Violation of the program rules or coupon terms may result in revocation of membership. Terms & Conditions Click Here to Sign Up       







